@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000/api
@authToken = <REEMPLAZA_CON_TU_TOKEN_DE_ACCESO>

### ------------------------------------------------------------------------
### 1. AUTENTICACIÓN
### ------------------------------------------------------------------------

### Login (Obtener Token)
# Usuario y contraseña mockeados en AuthController
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
    "username": "admin",
    "password": "admin123"
}

### Refresh Token
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
    "refresh": "<TU_REFRESH_TOKEN>"
}


### ------------------------------------------------------------------------
### 2. MODELOS
### ------------------------------------------------------------------------

### Listar Modelos
GET {{baseUrl}}/modelos
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Accept: application/json

### Crear Modelo
POST {{baseUrl}}/modelos
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
    "nombre": "MT-07",
    "marca": "Yamaha",
    "anio": "2024",
    "tipo_motor": "gasolina",
    "cilindrada": "689cc",
    "precio": 180000.00,
    "colores": ["azul", "negro"],
    "imagen": "https://example.com/mt-07.jpg"
}

### Buscar Modelos
GET {{baseUrl}}/modelos/search?query=Yamaha
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Accept: application/json


### ------------------------------------------------------------------------
### 3. INVENTARIO
### ------------------------------------------------------------------------

### Listar Inventario
GET {{baseUrl}}/inventario
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Accept: application/json

### Crear Item Inventario (Necesitas un ID de modelo válido)
POST {{baseUrl}}/inventario
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
    "modelo_id": "<ID_DEL_MODELO_CREADO_ARRIBA>",
    "color": "azul",
    "serie": "SERIE12345",
    "motor": "MOTOR12345",
    "vin": "VIN12345678901234",
    "estado": "disponible"
}

### Conteo Inventario
GET {{baseUrl}}/inventario/conteo
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Accept: application/json


